{"tid":486520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山女困引水道 老公靠GPS尋妻","createTime":"2017-12-02T02:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T02:54:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"748243cb80ea0dce582fcee37cb5b6d6c8606294","tid":486520,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232631\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232631&d=Mqva%2FuzIZq0EH9%2BEaea77G6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=cff1f403\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F20232631&h=ec8b8802\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171202/20232631</a><br />\n<br />\n行山女困引水道<br />\n老公靠GPS尋妻<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌姓曹（31歲）女子報稱不開心，昨晨8時許獨自離家，到青山公路近華員邨一帶郊遊散心，惟遲遲仍未回家，其姓黎（30歲）丈夫根據GPS定位發現妻子在青山公路葵涌段一山坡，於是前往尋找，惟遍尋不果，至晚上10時許報警求助。消防員接報到場，於引水道對落數米的位置尋獲女事主，原來她意外失足跌落引水道，腳部受傷，由消防員救起，交由救護車送院治理。"}]}